In CRM Analytics, create a column in a Data Prep recipe that displays the current date and time in a specified format.
REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS
To create a recipe: Edit CRM Analytics Dataflows OR Edit Dataset Recipes
This transformation works without interacting with any other columns.
Select Now in a Transform node of a Data Prep recipe.
Select the date format.
Optionally, change the label of the column that stores the Now data in the Column Label field.
Click Apply to add the transformation to the Transform node.
The Preview tab shows the new Now column.
To view the Graph area, click the Collapse button.
Save the recipe.
The Now option uses the date and time when the recipe last ran, based on UTC timezone.
title: Formatting Current Date and Time in CRM Analytics Data Prep
